"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Bitcoin in 2022\\n\\nTechnical analysis of the Bitcoin chart shows that the MacD index has entered the green zone from the red range, and Bitcoin has the ability to face a 5.5-fold increase. This month, the indicators that predict the rise of Bitcoin have not been few, and the fundamental situation of the network is also promising.\\n\\nThe last time the MacDay index was in this situation was in October 2020, when the value of bitcoin rose about 5.5 times from $ 11,500. If history repeats itself, we will probably see the price of Bitcoin cross the $ 220,000 mark in early 2022.\\n\\n\\\"I think we will soon see the beginning of a period of rapid rise in the price of bitcoin,\\\" said Anthony Pampliano, founder of the Morgan Craig Institute. The same thing happened in 2017, and the price of bitcoin rose from $ 10,000 to $ 20,000 in just 18 days. It would not be foolish to hope that this will happen later this year or early next year.\\n\\nBitcoin is back in the uptrend after falling sharply last month, during which its price halved from $ 62,000, and its value has increased by about 20% in recent months. Although Bitcoin is currently battling to conquer the $ 50,000 channel, the indicators, especially the moving average indicators, contain good news for Bitcoin in the coming days.\",\"timestamp\":1639134500,\"title\":\"Opinion\"},\"digest\":\"_ripA8tYuJh6V-IIuF8NYlFC8bijSM2I-3MBYE-EgkQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x93CeA28A9f9301b035b5F802c885b8893a6DC72A\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8Lr-XRB2J5n6LSyezE_Kol6pCIdiXo0hw2VgCQD5LRE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"TgfJydcI4b2xZIBO7G83mnJxgFOzOF_W6dFO2lQ4WpQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"a8ffCl-Hc5hHr-QVqrqengzl3Wj26FVrgHyDTABZcvvI3d0t76DrpZ1GCBxm28a-R1vyeWwxVjbYwch8EgLT7g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xf224b337d1a4e77cb662f2c776f5f9d98e8d1399d59d172c9978176ed8bc9e4143a85cf023de0b925e3dad4159a18aa5ca0d3f91fa2b3